Package com.telenav.kivakit.core.resource.path

Interface ResourcePathed

  • All Known Subinterfaces:
    FileService, FileSystemObjectService, FolderService, NetworkResource, Resource, WritableResource
    All Known Implementing Classes:
    BaseHttpResource, BaseNetworkResource, BaseReadableResource, BaseWritableResource, BitArrayResource, File, FtpResource, HdfsFile, HdfsFolder, HttpGetResource, HttpPostResource, HttpPutResource, InputResource, NullResource, OutputResource, PackageResource, ResourceSection, S3File, S3FileSystemObject, S3Folder, SecureFtpResource, SecureHttpGetResource, SecureHttpPostResource, StringResource, ZipEntry
    public interface ResourcePathed
    An object which has a ResourcePath, as returned by path(). Convenience methods provide access to the path's filename and extension(s).
    Author:
    jonathanl (shibo)
